{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/About_the_game.png?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome cadets!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s time to team up with fellow ghost hunters and take a stand against the mischievous ghosts hiding across the galaxy. Travel through wacky worlds and dizzying dimensions in search of these troublemakers before they cause even more havoc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spook-A-Boo is a couch co-op game for one to four players and can be played online or offline. Coordinate with your friends and family to outsmart your spooky foes, and capture them before they escape. Race against time in 30 unique levels to complete your mission and uncover the truth behind the ghosts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're a seasoned gamer or just looking for a fun family activity, Spook-A-Boo promises laughter, cooperation, and a whole lot of ghostly good times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/Chase.gif?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use Cutting-edge Tech</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip yourselves with the latest ghost-hunting gear to catch those pesky specters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/Gadgets.gif?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Encounter a Diverse Variety of Ghosts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These ghosts come in all shapes and sizes, their powers wacky and dangerous. Make sure that you catch them and not the other way around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/Electric.gif?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overcome Obstacles Together</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Communicate, collaborate and strategise with your teammates to triumph through everything the 5 unique worlds throw at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/LevelMechanics.gif?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dive into the Chaos of Spook-A-Boo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/extras/PlayerKick.gif?t=1736056629\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Please note that additional controllers would be required to play this game in local multiplayer mode.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736056629","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736056629","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/9ca8b4e95a4263f2041617162fd062ec6e0e15a9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736056629","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154150/9ca8b4e95a4263f2041617162fd062ec6e0e15a9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736056629","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Remote Pl